file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        critical: {type: string}
        high: {type: string}
        hostname: {type: string}
        info: {type: string}
        low: {type: string}
        medium: {type: string}
        score: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp1:
      properties:
        result: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes: {}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Tenable Nessus Vulnerability Scanner
  title: Tenable Nessus Vulnerability Scanner
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Launches Nessus Scan based on IP and Scan ID
      parameters:
      - description: Alternative IP targets for scan. Will scan these IPs instead
          of the scan configured ones
        example: 192.168.1.1, 192.168.0.1
        in: query
        name: Alt IP Targets
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: The ID of the Nessus scan you want to run
        example: '6'
        in: query
        name: Scan ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Nessus Scan
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Stops a Nessus Scan from Scan ID
      parameters:
      - description: The ID of the Nessus scan you want to stop
        example: '6'
        in: query
        name: Scan ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Nessus Stop Scan
tags:
- {name: Vulnerability & Patch Management}
